98point6 | Seattle, WA | Onsite | Multiple Positions | https://www.98point6.com/

At 98point6 we are reimagining the future of primary care through in-app messaging and by pairing physician experience with AI and automation. We've recently raised a $50m Series-C and last month launched in all 50 US states.

We're moving quickly in the digital health space and hiring for numerous positions. Open engineering roles include:

- Software Engineer, Data Engineering - Senior Software Engineer, Machine Learning - Manual Test Engineer - Mobile Software Engineer - iOS/Android - Back End Software Engineer - Senior Back End Software Engineer - Front End Software Engineer - Senior Front End Software Engineer - Senior Software Engineer, Infrastructure - Site Reliability Engineer (SRE) - Support Engineer

If you're interested please email me grinich [AT] 98point6.com or apply directly at our careers page: https://www.98point6.com/about/careers/.
